THE BEST OF CALIFORNIA COMES TO NEW YORK?

This list is just a sampling of our large, superlative selection of California wines. From Napa and Sonoma in the North -- to Temecula in the South --

we have tried to make it reflect the incredible breadth and diversity of California wine-making. Here you will find good, inexpensive table wines that are wonderful for daily drinking -- along with rare, magnificent Cabernets and Chardonnays that would honor a serious wine cellar anywhere in the world.
